Alice Cocéa https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alice_Coc%C3%A9a 0 Alice Sophie Cocéa or Cocea (28 July 1899 – 2 July 1970) was a Romanian-born French actress and singer. She was the sister of socialist journalist and novelist N. D. Cocea, and the aunt of actresses Dina and Tantzi Cocea.
